<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-ng-app="canvas">
<head>
  %= include 'header.inc', title => 'Korora Project'
</head>
<body>
  %= include 'noscript.inc'

  <div class="page-container">

    %= include 'website/navigation.inc', active => 'discover'

    <div class="page-content">
      <!-- CONTENT -->

      <div id="page-discover" class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
              <div class="btn-group pull-right">
                <a href="https://plus.google.com/+KororaProjectOrg" class="btn btn-xs btn-default btn-google-plus"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-google-plus"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/kororaproject" class="btn btn-xs btn-default btn-facebook"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/kororaproject" class="btn btn-xs btn-default btn-twitter"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-twitter"></i></a>
              </div>
              <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/discover">Discover</a></li>
              <li class="active">Cinnamon</li>
            </ol>
            <h1 class="text-center"><strong>Discover.</strong> The Cinnamon Desktop</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="text-center">
              <img class="img-responsive img-showcase" src="/img/screenshots/korora-cinnamon-desktop-apps.jpg" alt="Cinnamon Desktop">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hr"></div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <h2 class="center">Traditional layout, advanced features, easy to use, powerful, flexible</h2>
            <p>Cinnamon is built on top of core GNOME technologies like GTK and Clutter yet provides a more traditional desktop while still including modern advanced features. More akin to KDE and unlike GNOME, it is designed to be very flexible and configurable. Together these things make it a great desktop option!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hr"></div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <img class="img-responsive img-showcase" src="/img/screenshots/korora-cinnamon-apps.jpg" alt="Cinnamon Applications Menu">
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Tradition still reigns</h2>
            <p>The applications menu uses a traditional category system to divide up applications, but also includes handy favourites right there in the menu. Preferences, administration, places as well as shortcuts to logout and power tasks are readily available.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- END CONTENT -->
    </div>
  </div>

  %= include 'website/footer.inc'

  <!-- MODALS -->
  %= include 'authenticate.inc'

  <!-- SCRIPTS -->
  %= include 'scripts.inc'

</body>
</html>
